&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The position of Mahima from the front end is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;28&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The position of Anshul from the rear end is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;22&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;nd&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;People in between Mahima and Anshul =&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;According to the given information, the diagram will be,&lt;/p&gt;

